repository.name: kubernetes-microservices
repository.description: This is NodeJS based application designed to showcase microservices hosted in local Docker or Kubernetes with local docker registry images. Application contains 1x WebApp service + 2x REST API services where one of the service is internal which is not directly accessible from internet.
